				<title>API Products are Products</title>
				<ul>
					<li>Products have <em>consumers</em> and should drive organizational value</li>
					<li><em>API Products</em> are a special kind of product with additional constraints</li>
					<ul>
						<li>More a <em>service</em> than a (physical) product</li>
						<li>Many APIs are not (directly) consumed by external consumers</li>
						<li>API products are the parts for composing digital value chains</li>
					</ul>
